In `src/app/api/cron/process-installments/route.ts` and `src/app/api/cron/process-statements/route.ts`:
1. Import: `import { timingSafeEqual } from 'crypto';`
2. Replace the token check:
   ```typescript
   const secret = process.env.CRON_SECRET;
   if (!token || !secret || token.length !== secret.length ||
       !timingSafeEqual(Buffer.from(token), Buffer.from(secret))) {
     return NextResponse.json({ error: 'Unauthorized' }, { status: 401 });
   }
   ```

In `src/lib/auth.ts`:
1. Add a startup guard at the top of the file (before the `betterAuth()` call):
   ```typescript
   if (!process.env.BETTER_AUTH_SECRET) {
     throw new Error('BETTER_AUTH_SECRET environment variable is required');
   }
   ```
2. Pass the secret explicitly in the `betterAuth()` config:
   ```typescript
   export const auth = betterAuth({
     secret: process.env.BETTER_AUTH_SECRET,
     // ... rest of existing config unchanged
   });
   ```
